hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Another year dapsone hypersensitivity syndrome medscape Why is there not even one picture in your report or one video to show the 100s of killings of the innocent civilians and the police forces at the hands of the MB and Morsi supporters who are heavily armed and wandering the streets in Egypt spewing hate and terrorizing innocent civilians. Not one picture of the 10s of churches, orphanages and community centers that have been burned and the Government buildings that have been torched and destroyed? don’t you think you are missing something?
